📊 Retry Summary
├── Retried: ${pre_retry_progress.counts.failed} modules
├── Recovered: ${pre_retry_progress.counts.failed - post_retry_progress.counts.failed}
├── Still Failed: ${post_retry_progress.counts.failed}
└── Final Status: ${post_retry_progress.counts.completed}/${sub_prd_groups.length} completed

